  <brief_title>Phase 3 Study of OTO-201 in Acute Otitis Externa</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Randomized, Double-Blind, Sham-Controlled, Multicenter, Phase 3 Study of OTO-201 Given as a Single Administration for Treatment of Acute Otitis Externa</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
